Classroom mode:
On JoinClassroom(classroom_id: string):
  user.classroom_id = classroom_id
  FetchLeaderboard(classroom_id)  // From cloud/local server

Function UpdateLeaderboard():
  If user.classroom_id:
    Send user.xp to server
    leaderboard = GetLeaderboard(user.classroom_id)
    UpdateSidePanelLeaderboard(leaderboard)

  // Weekly reset logic
  If isMonday() and time > 9:00 AM:
    ResetWeeklyLeaderboard()
    If user.rank == 1:
      GrantAchievement("team_leader")
